        <div class="msgSubject">Dragoon</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-07-15 04:03:23   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-127918820345085165" id="quote-127918820345085165" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-127918820345085165" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=186&amp;mid=127918820345085165&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=127918820345085165&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_127918820345085165" onclick="followToggle('add','127918820345085165')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
