      <div class="msgContentFrame">Not to sound negative or anything but maybe your overlooking one fundamental issue? FFXIV, despite its undeniable links to FFXI, is inactual fact a new game (per sae). So perhaps Enix has not desire or future plans to implement a &quot;Dragon master&quot; ability / class. <br /> <br /> Maybe a Lancer is just a 2 handed weapon wielding dps class that attacks from a greater distance than say a Gladiator?. <br /> <br /> Again not meaning to sound negative but perhaps such differences are needed for this game, if not it might as well just be called FFXI-2!</div>
